# Expected: returns match with EBM GOP code(s) for MR modality
# Source system: DICOM CID 29 Modality (http://dicom.nema.org/resources/ontology/DCM)
# @name ebm_translate_mr
GET http://localhost:8080/fhir/ConceptMap/$translate?url=https://fhir.cognovis.de/imaging/ConceptMap/imaging-study-to-ebm-gop&code=MR&system=http://dicom.nema.org/resources/ontology/DCM
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

